{"title":"我们是革命的铁路工人（对口词）","authors":["宁宝才"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":2,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是革命的铁路工人（对口词）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼和浩特铁路局电务工程队通信工　宁宝才"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是革命的铁路工人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗在运输线上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的性格、形象，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟火车头一模一样："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有钢打铁铸的骨头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有冲锋陷阵的胆量；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满腔熊熊烈火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身热气红光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干活雷厉风行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲话高门大嗓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一不怕苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲十足充沛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二不怕死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗志无比坚强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南征北战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不离轨道；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚跟不乱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站稳立场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹雨打不迷路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头脑中有鲜明的方向。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是革命的铁路工人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想来武装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们懂得，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己工作的意义。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的工人该怎么当。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚守祖国钢铁运输线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为社会主义革命推波助浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦练过硬本领，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手中的工具就是战斗的枪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产高潮激流勇进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车机工电人强马壮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比学赶帮超势如破竹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五好竞赛如滔滔巨浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋头苦干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚持三老四严。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忠心赤胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做到四个一样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打一颗道钉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿出对党的忠诚；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺一根枕木，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要为六亿人民着想。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了成绩绝不骄傲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百尺竿头青云直上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国要造汽车银鹰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们送铁送钢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国要盖高楼广厦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们拉砖运梁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国在攀登工业高峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们送上煤炭、机床。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社儿女跟自然开战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们送上化肥、犁杖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千座高山为社会主义献宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们送去钻头、风枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万顷沙原要交出棉粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们送去种子、苗秧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有志青年要去广阔天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们送他上山下乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把北京的收音机送到西藏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把兴安岭的木材运到黄浦江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大寨的玉米、大庆的油，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云鄂博的矿石、广州的糖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往上装，往上放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往上放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往上装！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运往塞北江南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送到四面八方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让所有的人力物资，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为社会主义发热发光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是革命的铁路工人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党给了无穷的智慧和力量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红心为祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两眼更把世界望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五大洲的风云在胸中激荡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚非拉的雷霆在耳边喧响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援阶级兄弟义不容辞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界革命的责任担在肩上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的时代需要高速度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们就多装、快跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快跑、多装！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大开汽门，火力加旺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜兼程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目标："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正前方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山拦路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水挡道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地陷下去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们填！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天塌下来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们扛！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇见牛鬼蛇神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有豺狼虎豹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碾成泥浆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千重困难脚下踩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万般障碍一扫光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有我铁路工人在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进的车轮谁敢挡！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有我铁路工人在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进的车轮谁敢挡！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}